<P>
 ART OF FILM: You've seen John Alvin's work, even if you don't know the 
Northridge artist's name. He drew the posters for Disney's current animated 
smash "The Lion King" and "E.T." He's known for packing a poster with human 
emotion, using such contemporary tools as an airbrush and a computer. Valley 
Life! Page 3 
