<HEADLINE>
<P>
DIGEST: LANDTISER IS HEADED FOR SAN ANTONIO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JOHN ORTEGA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Rob Landtiser, the fifth-place finisher in the 400-meter intermediate hurdles 
for College of the Canyons in the State Junior College track and field 
championships, will attend Texas San Antonio. 
</P>
<P>
 Landtiser, who won the Western State Conference title, has a best of 52.76 
seconds. JOHN ORTEGA 
</P>
