<BYLINE>
<P>
By JASON GRANT 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Police are searching for a gunman who fatally shot a 23-year-old Ventura man 
early Thursday morning in the bedroom of the suspect's girlfriend. 
</P>
<P>
 Roger Rowland died at Ventura County Medical Center about 45 minutes after he 
was shot in the stomach in an apartment on Kirk Avenue in Ventura, authorities 
said. 
</P>
<P>
 Ventura police are continuing to hunt for Thomas Al Corral, 23, the suspected 
gunman. They are also looking for Ruben Viveros, 19, who accompanied Corral to 
the apartment complex. 
</P>
