 Shortly after midnight, Corral forced his way at gunpoint into the apartment 
of his 18-year-old girlfriend, the mother of his infant child, police said. 
Corral threatened the woman's younger brother and entered a bedroom, where he 
fired several shots at Rowland, hitting him once in the abdomen, police said. 
</P>
