<P>
 Amoco to Trim Staff by 4,500: The Chicago-based oil company is restructuring 
to pare its bureaucracy. The reduction of nearly 10% of its work force will 
make Amoco Corp., the nation's fifth-largest oil company, a leaner competitor 
in an era of stable oil prices and computer-driven cost efficiency, Chairman H. 
