</P>
<P>
 "They are nosy. They're always asking me a million questions whenever I go 
anywhere. I guess they're just looking out for me, but it still gets on my 
nerves." 
</P>
<P>
 Sophomore, 15 
</P>
<P>
 Cypress 
</P>
</TEXT>
