<P>
 Crossing guards -- An article Thursday on the Laguna Niguel City Council's 
decision to put crossing guards near two schools incorrectly listed a location. 
Guards will be at Ridgeway Avenue and Niguel Road temporarily. None will be at 
Ridgeway and Charles Road. 
</P>
